                        <interp inst="t18490507-name-329" type="given" value="LIGOINER"></interp>LIGOINER THOMAS</persName>
                  </hi> I am clerk to Mr. Hodgson—the prisoner has not accounted to me for this 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. or 8<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> Was he to settle for the beer before the bottles were brought home? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> If paid for on delivery.(The prisoner received a good character).</p>
